{
  "skill_version": "1.0.0",
  "skill": {
    "name": "vision-analyzer",
    "description": "先进的计算机视觉分析助手，支持物体检测、OCR 文字识别、场景理解、图像描述和人脸分析",
    "version": "1.8.0",
    "author": "VisionAI",
    "category": "vision",
    "tags": ["视觉", "图像", "OCR", "识别", "计算机视觉", "AI"],
    "price": 0.025,
    "integration": {
      "type": "function",
      "config": {
        "systemPrompt": "You are a computer vision expert capable of analyzing images with high accuracy and detail.\n\nYour capabilities:\n1. Object detection and recognition\n2. Text extraction (OCR)\n3. Scene and context understanding\n4. Image description and captioning\n5. Visual quality assessment\n6. Content moderation\n\nAnalysis Approach:\n- Start with overall scene description\n- Identify main subjects and objects\n- Note spatial relationships\n- Extract any visible text\n- Assess image quality and characteristics\n- Provide confidence levels for detections\n\nOutput Format:\n1. Scene Overview: Brief description of what's in the image\n2. Objects Detected: List with confidence scores\n3. Text Content: Any OCR results\n4. Visual Attributes: Colors, composition, style\n5. Context/Interpretation: What the image represents\n6. Quality Notes: Blur, lighting, resolution issues\n\nBe objective and precise. If uncertain, indicate confidence level.",
        "functions": [
          {
            "name": "analyze_image",
            "description": "分析图像内容",
            "parameters": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "image_url": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "图像 URL 或 base64"
                },
                "analysis_type": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "分析类型",
                  "enum": ["general", "objects", "text", "faces", "scenes"],
                  "default": "general"
                }
              },
              "required": ["image_url"]
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "extract_text",
            "description": "从图像中提取文字 (OCR)",
            "parameters": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "image_url": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "图像 URL 或 base64"
                },
                "language": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "文字语言",
                  "default": "auto"
                }
              },
              "required": ["image_url"]
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "detect_objects",
            "description": "检测图像中的物体",
            "parameters": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "image_url": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "图像 URL 或 base64"
                },
                "confidence_threshold": {
                  "type": "number",
                  "description": "置信度阈值",
                  "default": 0.5
                }
              },
              "required": ["image_url"]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "tools": [
      {
        "name": "analyze_image",
        "description": "分析图像内容",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "image_url": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "图像 URL"
            },
            "features": {
              "type": "array",
              "description": "分析特征",
              "items": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": ["objects", "text", "faces", "scenes", "colors"]
              }
            }
          },
          "required": ["image_url"]
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "extract_text",
        "description": "OCR 文字识别",
        "parameters": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "image_url": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "图像 URL"
            }
          },
          "required": ["image_url"]
        }
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "input": "分析这张图片中的内容...",
        "output": "图像分析结果：\n1. 场景：室内办公环境\n2. 检测到：笔记本电脑 (95%)、咖啡杯 (88%)..."
      }
    ]
  }
}
